### Bug Identification and Reporting â€“ Aruba AP (500 Series)
Identified a band steering bug in specific Aruba AP 500 Series models running a particular ArubaOS version.

Analyzed client connectivity issues and isolated the root cause related to band steering behavior under dual-band environments.

Raised a TAC case with Aruba Support and coordinated with the vendor for resolution.

Documented the affected models and firmware versions, and notified the internal team to avoid deploying those OS versions in production.

The discovery directly contributed to improved OS upgrade planning and stability of future wireless deployments.